citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:42:24.000Z","msg":"路透社報導，週一美國將會進一步收緊對華為的制裁，除非獲得特別許可，否則華為不可購買由外國公司生產但採用了美國軟件或技術的半導體產品。而且將新增38間華為關聯公司入黑名單，因此總名單達到152間。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:44:02.000Z","msg":"38間公司中，有部分位於香港。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:26:46.000Z","msg":"無先出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab97d8aea6cc5fb595603a36b502dbd0d4bfaf2a","tid":2161133,"uid":22440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:27:15.000Z","msg":"清朝d官都未識走資<br />\n制裁有春用咩<br />\n今時今日對佢地黎講美國仲親過中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9b9cb1f419717a2a019007313ff91c9aeb513c","tid":2161133,"uid":255637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"70ef5a7145956bcd8b8fa39771c9b4111b341809","tid":2161133,"uid":293677,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bd73191e2ab30e51d36c859136eaf0ccec728711","tid":2161133,"uid":37058,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:38:11.000Z","msg":"讓暴風雨唔知乜柒吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q1Ejf5F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ1Ejf5F.jpg&h=78439e05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:27:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那d水位依家越黎越高"},{"pid":"51be6b19372aaf98367d60736ec6cfd255655c43","tid":2161133,"uid":239336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:28:45.000Z","msg":"華為同習大大：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PgjSBcv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPgjSBcv.gif&h=de40efac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"261e2e047fa63914f484f576e433c75cd23f54c1","tid":2161133,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:29:05.000Z","msg":"正式公告<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.state.gov/the-united-states-further-restricts-huawei-access-to-u-s-technology/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Fthe-united-states-further-restricts-huawei-access-to-u-s-technology%2F&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21JE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=ab73de1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.state.gov/the-united-states-further-restricts-huawei-access-to-u-s-technology/</a><br />\n<br />\n商務部封殺咗一啲繞過制裁既方法<br />\n<br />\nThe Department of State strongly supports the Commerce Department&rsquo;s expansion today of its Foreign Direct Product Rule, which will prevent Huawei from circumventing U.S. law through alternative chip production and provision of off-the-shelf (OTS) chips produced with tools acquired from the United States. This measure follows the more limited expansion of the Foreign Direct Product Rule in May, which Huawei has continuously tried to evade.<br />\n<br />\n加多38間華為既相關公司入制裁名單<br />\n<br />\nThe Commerce Department also added 38 Huawei affiliates to its Entity List, which identifies foreign parties prohibited from receiving certain sensitive technologies and allowed Huawei&rsquo;s Temporary General License (TGL) to expire. The United States has provided ample time for affected companies and persons &ndash; primarily Huawei customers &ndash; to identify and shift to other sources of equipment, software, and technology and wind-down their operations. Now that time is up.<br />\n<br />\nWe will not tolerate efforts by the CCP to undermine the privacy of our citizens, our businesses&rsquo; intellectual property, or the integrity of next-generation networks worldwide.<br />\n<br />\n司法部告鳩佢<br />\n<br />\nWe are backing up our words with actions across the U.S. Government. The Department of Justice has indicted Huawei for stealing U.S. technology, conspiracy, wire fraud, bank fraud, racketeering, and helping Iran to evade sanctions, amongst other charges. The Department of Commerce placed Huawei on the Entity List in 2019. The Department of State has engaged in vigorous diplomacy for more than a year to share what we know about Huawei and other untrustworthy vendors with allies and partners around the world.<br />\n<br />\nThe United States will continue to restrict most U.S. exports to Huawei and its affiliates on the Entity List for activities that threaten U.S. national security and international stability. We urge our allies and partners to join us."},{"pid":"385ee9a6133ff3868367c8562c7f65b5f1f4a3af","tid":2161133,"uid":333287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d2442a17d0166e153337c4445481e94b828ed2b0","tid":2161133,"uid":48040,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:42:24.000Z","msg":"路透社報導，週一美國將會進一步收緊對華為的制裁，除非獲得特別許可，否則華為不可購買由外國公司生產但採用了美國軟件或技術的半導體產品。而且將新增38間華為關聯公司入黑名單，因此總名單達到152間。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:31:00.000Z","msg":"MTK:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0a8501807d8a3e9d53f49c2597cb963173565d","tid":2161133,"uid":307398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371cfa22e3df704ac05d48d2165f5ed35dc64075","tid":2161133,"uid":28277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:32:06.000Z","msg":"係我哋唔做你美國佬生意，係我哋制裁美國佬，唔係美國制裁華為，責任在於美方"},{"pid":"cd117ed49bb718c1e294734f58947b5bbb6d9f26","tid":2161133,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:36:11.000Z","ms